"'''The Monster'''" was a short story by [[Daniel Wallace]], originally published in [[Star Wars Gamer 2|''Star Wars Gamer'' 2]], and later released on [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]]. It takes place in [[36 BBY/Legends|36 BBY]] on [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]].

==Plot summary==
After a beached [[Sando aqua monster/Legends|sando aqua monster]] uncovers a hidden facility, [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Quarsh Panaka/Legends|Quarsh Panaka]] tracks a fleeing revolutionary to it. Little does he know, the facility holds a dark secret stretching to the highest levels of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo's]] government.

